posting_body: ["Embrace classic comfort and contemporary style at 3300 Tamarac Apartments, in Denver's Hampden neighborhood.", 'Our collection of refined studio, 1 & 2 bedroom apartments offer you a place to rest, relax, and have a little fun.', 'From our relaxed modern style and upscale social spaces to chic interiors, youll be ready to unwind in no time.', '-Fenced dog park with pet watering station', '-Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms', '-Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance', '-Oversized closets', '-Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas', '-3 relaxing pools with expansive sundecks', '-Onsite playground', '-Easy access to public transportation', '-Elevator access', '-Indoor racquetball courts', '-Energy efficient appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher                                                                                                                                select units                                                                                                                                Featured amenity', '-Reserved covered parking                                                                                    Photo                                                                                                                                 Featured amenity', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
